description:
“Startling Prophecies for America” is an eye-opening, straight-forward, well-researched and easy-to-understand series of talks explaining the prophecy of Revelation 13 about a leopard-like “beast” (verses 1-10), a lamb-like “beast” (verse 11), and how both beasts cooperate together to enforce the mark of the beast (verses 12-16) during earth’s final crisis. Part 2 of 3. Updated 2020 version.
